d-2a_{3}-a_{4}=a_{4}\mathbf{4}^{+}\left(\mathbf{3}^{-}+\mathbf{5}^{-}-2\mathbf{2}^{-}\right)\quad(a_{1}=0)\label{eq:ex2-IBP4}\\
