\begin_layout Standard
此区域中
\begin_inset Formula $k\sim q,\:l_{0}\sim y/q,\:\mathbf{l}\sim\sqrt{y}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula $k-l\sim k$
\end_inset

