Potential-potential region
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在此区域中
\begin_inset Formula $k_{0},l_{0}\sim\lambda^{2}q$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{k},\mathbf{l}\sim\lambda q$
\end_inset

