的无标度积分，直到
\begin_inset Formula $k_{0}$
\end_inset

 regular为止。总之只需考虑
\begin_inset Formula $k_{0}=\pm\left|\mathbf{k}\right|,k_{0}=\pm\left|\mathbf{k}+\mathbf{p}-\mathbf{p}'\right|$
\end_inset

