 & =\frac{e^{\epsilon\gamma_{\text{E}}}}{q^{2}}\int\frac{d^{d-1}k}{\pi^{d/2-1}}\left(\frac{1}{\left|\mathbf{k}\right|^{3}\left[\mathbf{k}^{2}-\left(\mathbf{k}+\mathbf{p}-\mathbf{p}'\right)^{2}+i0\right]}-\frac{1}{\left|\mathbf{k}+\mathbf{p}-\mathbf{p}'\right|^{3}\left[\mathbf{k}^{2}-\left(\mathbf{k}+\mathbf{p}-\mathbf{p}'\right)^{2}+i0\right]}\right)\label{eq:ex3-Is}
\end{align}

\end_inset

关于上式两项中为何都取
\begin_inset Formula $+i0$
\end_inset

，这里有一个
\series bold
要点
\series default
：如果按照传播子自然的取法，第二项中应该是
\begin_inset Formula $-i0$
\end_inset

